N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.38 - Failure to comply with discovery

State Regulations

The Board may issue orders for appropriate relief if any
party fails to comply with any provision of sub-part D of these rules, including deeming a party's failure to comply with any provision of sub-part D
of these rules as a waiver of the right to further participation in the
proceeding. Notes
